        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "{\"success\":true,\"process_rule_id\":\"J09B\",\"process_rule\":\"1. **Copy decision table into table J09B_temp where the tour starts with J09B** (Task: Copy decision table into table J09B_temp where the tour starts with J09B).\\n2. **Add ENTSCHEIDUNG column** (Task: Add ENTSCHEIDUNG column).\\n3. **Classify meter reading type** (Task: Classify meter reading type). Apply the following rules to set the `ENTSCHEIDUNG` column:\\n    *   Set `ENTSCHEIDUNG` to \\\"KSA\\\" when a `HAUS` has less than 3 `EQUNR`.\\n    *   ELSE set `ENTSCHEIDUNG` to \\\"EVU\\\".\\n    *   SET all houses with `HOUSE_NUM1` of 0 to \\\"EVU\\\".\\n4. **JOIN table with EABLG table using INSTALLATION** (Task: JOIN table with EABLG table using INSTALLATION).\\n5. **JOIN table with SALES_MASTER and NET_MASTER** (Task: JOIN table with SALES_MASTER and NET_MASTER). Use the following join rule: JOIN table with NET_MASTER and SALES_MASTER table using `EQUNR`.\\n6. **Compare customer sales master data and net master data** (Task: Compare customer sales master data and net master data).\\n7. **Check if sales customer data is NOT empty**:\\n    *   **If True:** Use sales customer data table entries (Task: Use sales customer data table entries).\\n    *   **Else:** Use net data customer table entries (Task: Use net data customer table entries).\\n8. **Export the final data from the table as CSV file named J09B** (Task: Export the final data from the table as CSV file named J09B). Use the following column names for export: `Meter Reading (MR) Doc. No.`, `HAUS`, `ANLAGE`, `ME_MA_ID`, `EQUNR`, `HOUSE_NUM1`, `ENTSCHEIDUNG`, `TITLE`, `FORENAME`, `SURNAME`, `STREET`, `STREETNO`, `POST_CODE1`, `CITY1`, `CITY2`, `EMAIL`.\\n9. **Send email with the CSV file to EVU** (Task: Send email with the CSV file to EVU). Use the following details: Email address `meter.readings@evu.com`, file path `<path_to_exported_csv_file>`.\\n10. **Delete temporary table** (Task: Delete temporary table).\"}",
            "id": "lc_a4c5adc5-d9cf-4416-baba-15902aec6189"
          }
        ],
        "type": "tool",
        "name": "retrieve_process",
        "id": "65e54462-c70a-4bd9-b521-32766d8f7176",
        "tool_call_id": "call_4iaz7y2x",
        "artifact": {
          "structured_content": {
            "success": true,
            "process_rule_id": "J09B",
            "process_rule": "1. **Copy decision table into table J09B_temp where the tour starts with J09B** (Task: Copy decision table into table J09B_temp where the tour starts with J09B).\n2. **Add ENTSCHEIDUNG column** (Task: Add ENTSCHEIDUNG column).\n3. **Classify meter reading type** (Task: Classify meter reading type). Apply the following rules to set the `ENTSCHEIDUNG` column:\n    *   Set `ENTSCHEIDUNG` to \"KSA\" when a `HAUS` has less than 3 `EQUNR`.\n    *   ELSE set `ENTSCHEIDUNG` to \"EVU\".\n    *   SET all houses with `HOUSE_NUM1` of 0 to \"EVU\".\n4. **JOIN table with EABLG table using INSTALLATION** (Task: JOIN table with EABLG table using INSTALLATION).\n5. **JOIN table with SALES_MASTER and NET_MASTER** (Task: JOIN table with SALES_MASTER and NET_MASTER). Use the following join rule: JOIN table with NET_MASTER and SALES_MASTER table using `EQUNR`.\n6. **Compare customer sales master data and net master data** (Task: Compare customer sales master data and net master data).\n7. **Check if sales customer data is NOT empty**:\n    *   **If True:** Use sales customer data table entries (Task: Use sales customer data table entries).\n    *   **Else:** Use net data customer table entries (Task: Use net data customer table entries).\n8. **Export the final data from the table as CSV file named J09B** (Task: Export the final data from the table as CSV file named J09B). Use the following column names for export: `Meter Reading (MR) Doc. No.`, `HAUS`, `ANLAGE`, `ME_MA_ID`, `EQUNR`, `HOUSE_NUM1`, `ENTSCHEIDUNG`, `TITLE`, `FORENAME`, `SURNAME`, `STREET`, `STREETNO`, `POST_CODE1`, `CITY1`, `CITY2`, `EMAIL`.\n9. **Send email with the CSV file to EVU** (Task: Send email with the CSV file to EVU). Use the following details: Email address `meter.readings@evu.com`, file path `<path_to_exported_csv_file>`.\n10. **Delete temporary table** (Task: Delete temporary table)."
          }
        },
        "status": "success"
      }
